'''Sofía Castro Ríos''' (born 18 September 1970) is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] lawyer and politician affiliated with the [[Institutional Revolutionary Party]]. As of 2014 he served as Deputy of the [[LIX Legislature of the Mexican Congress|LIX]] and [[LXI Legislature of the Mexican Congress|LXI]] Legislatures of the Mexican Congress representing [[Oaxaca]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Perfil del legislador|url=http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Librerias/pp_PerfilLegislador.php?SID=&Referencia=569951|publisher=Legislative Information System|accessdate=3 May 2014}}</ref>

